  framework_3 = "Lamport (1978) happens-before — already cited by axis-J for supersession ordering. CITED-AND-MOVED-ON: axis-K extends Lamport's ordering primitive from death-side (axis-J) to birth-side; we still use a STATIC date stamp, not a vector clock; no distributed-system semantics imported."
